2. 
In view of order passed by Apex Court in Criminal Appeal No.1503 of 2023 arising out of SLP (Criminal) No.3241 of 2023 (
Pradhani Jani vs. The State of Odisha
) and SLP (Criminal) No.7203 of 2023 (
Sajid vs. State of U.P.
), let this matter be placed before appropriate Bench after getting nomination from Hon'ble The Chief Justice, if possible, on 19.02.2024 as fresh.
